    {
      "id": "e7ebd9fd-0fc5-4e66-9936-ab780f7bc75a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors make a systematic literature review of over 140 studies in the area of student performance. Main aim of the paper is to identify what are the predictors, methods, time and aim of the prediction.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "e7ebd9fd-0fc5-4e66-9936-ab780f7bc75a",
        "parent": {
