    {
      "id": "cb7eda55-7ecf-4f8e-b9c7-b2f2cc142fba",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors also make a distinction between studies that aim to perform analysis of student performance on classroom based educational contexts. Msin gap that is identified is the lack of studies that focus on prediction of performance before the start of the course.",
